{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882321372,"sessionID":"ses_2852c4c11ffe0Ez5NgMweWeY4P","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad5bdaf0013fBNQw05Icb6jD","messageID":"msg_d7ad5a78b001q2xu4GshFqCGu9","sessionID":"ses_2852c4c11ffe0Ez5NgMweWeY4P","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-07445086abd94dbc81e4692652250daf","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/tasks.md","limit":50},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module**: `manifests`\n4: **Language**: YAML\n5: **Size**: M\n6: **Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n7: \n8: ## Task Breakdown\n9: \n10: ### Task 1: Review existing Workload Manager ServiceAccount template\n11: - [ ] Review manifests/charts/agentcube/templates/workload-manager/serviceaccount.yaml\n12: - [ ] Verify template includes proper Helm conditionals (enabled and serviceAccount.create)\n13: - [ ] Verify template uses correct helper functions (serviceAccountName, namespace, labels)\n14: - [ ] Verify component label is set to workload-manager\n15: - [ ] Verify annotations are conditionally included\n16: - [ ] Document any issues or missing elements\n17: \n18: **Verification**: Template follows best practices and matches component pattern\n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ### Task 2: Review existing Workload Manager RBAC template\n23: - [ ] Review manifests/charts/agentcube/templates/workload-manager/rbac.yaml\n24: - [ ] Verify ClusterRole is defined with proper metadata\n25: - [ ] Verify ClusterRoleBinding is defined with proper metadata\n26: - [ ] Verify rules reference .Values.rbac.clusterRole.rules\n27: - [ ] Verify subjects reference correct ServiceAccount\n28: - [ ] Verify roleRef references correct ClusterRole\n29: - [ ] Document any issues or missing elements\n30: \n31: **Verification**: Template matches delta-spec.md requirements for Workload Manager\n32: \n33: ---\n34: \n35: ### Task 3: Complete Workload Manager ClusterRole rules in values.yaml\n36: - [ ] Review manifests/charts/agentcube/values.yaml rbac.clusterRole.rules section\n37: - [ ] Verify rules include permissions for agent-sandbox resources\n38: - [ ] Verify rules include permissions for AgentRuntime CRDs (runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes)\n39: - [ ] Verify rules include permissions for CodeInterpreter CRDs (runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters)\n40: - [ ] Verify rules include permissions for status subresources\n41: - [ ] Verify rules include permissions for core workloads (pods, services, configmaps)\n42: - [ ] Verify rules include permissions for secrets (get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete)\n43: - [ ] Verify rules include permissions for events (create, patch)\n44: - [ ] Verify rules follow principle of least privilege (no wildcards unless necessary)\n45: - [ ] Add any missing permissions based on delta-spec.md requirements\n46: \n47: **Verification**: Workload Manager ClusterRole has all required permissions with minimal privileges\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 487. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) Tasks\n\n**Module**: `manifests`\n**Language**: YAML\n**Size**: M\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Review existing Workload Manager ServiceAccount template\n- [ ] Review manifests/charts/agentcube/templates/workload-manager/serviceaccount.yaml\n- [ ] Verify template includes proper Helm conditionals (enabled and serviceAccount.create)\n- [ ] Verify template uses correct helper functions (serviceAccountName, namespace, labels)\n- [ ] Verify component label is set to workload-manager\n- [ ] Verify annotations are conditionally included\n- [ ] Document any issues or missing elements\n\n**Verification**: Template follows best practices and matches component pattern\n\n---","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775882321356,"end":1775882321370}}}}
